trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged"></xref> events.

The ChildChangedEventArgs class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes when the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties change.
trans-unit.target: ChildChangedEventArgs 類別會由<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost>類別時的值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName>或<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName>屬性變更。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>
